<div class="header clearfix">
  <h3 class="page-header">Extensions</h3>
</div>

<p>LTI provides a great base for creating a connection between learning tools. These extensions are used to add functionality on top of that connection. These are unofficial and not all consumers and providers will support them.</p>

<hr>

<h3>Global Configurations</h3>

<table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-condensed">
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr>
    <td><%= link_to "Content", docs_path({section: "extensions", page: "content"}) %></td>
    <td>This extension is used to pass content to the tool consumer from the tool provider.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><%= link_to "Result Data", docs_path({section: "extensions", page: "result_data"}) %></td>
    <td>Add resultData in addition to resultScore in outcome services.</td>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

